    <h2>Why ASP.NET Core?</h2>
    <p>ASP.NET Core is a powerful, open-source framework for building modern web applications. Whether you're creating web APIs, single-page applications (SPAs), or full-fledged web apps, ASP.NET Core has the features you need to get your app up and running quickly, with robust performance and security.</p>

    <h3>Key Features of ASP.NET Core</h3> 
    <ul>
        <li>Cross-platform: Run your applications on Windows, Linux, or macOS.</li>
        <li>High performance: ASP.NET Core is optimized for fast execution.</li>
        <li>Modern development tools: Utilize powerful tools like Visual Studio and Visual Studio Code for a seamless development experience.</li>
        <li>Secure: Built-in features to protect your applications from the latest security threats.</li>
        <li>Cloud-ready: ASP.NET Core apps integrate well with cloud services like Azure.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Get Started Today</h3>
